name: “HEN ‘pocalypse Not!”
description: My contribution to the #HENpocalypse celebration of Version 2 of Hic Et Nunc started off as more than this. At some point, though, I realized that I had two pieces of art. Furthermore, I realized that I would do each of them a disservice by using one as the background of the other. In this piece, I started with pictures from a Molotov cocktail photo shoot of My treasured and much loved babygirl. I’m using them here to tell a visual story about the recent anxieties regarding a much-feared, world-ending conflagration. 1200x500 pixels (animated gif). Only 1.0 tez. Edition of 100. 17% royalty rate. Minted July 17th, 2021. Verify via Twitter account @tormential and/or Instagram account @_tormential_ and/or tormential.tez
